        "\\end{aligned}$$\n",
        "\n",
        "Since $f(x) = x^4$ is a polynomial of degree 4, the Legendre expansion will have at most 5 nonzero terms:\n",
        "\n",
        "$$f(x) = a_0 P_0(x) + a_1 P_1(x) + a_2 P_2(x) + a_3 P_3(x) + a_4 P_4(x)$$\n",
